scripts.name: Jekka for Tiktok (Part1)
scripts.description: Jekka is a leading AI chatbot worldwide. This script enables Jekka to assist you in responding to TikTok customer service messages, helping you efficiently manage customer demands and boost sales for your store. To use this script, you will need to integrate it with the Jekka chatbot management platform. For detailed instructions, please contact support@jekka.ai.
